ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Easy to deal high combo damage.', 'Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.']
DetailDes: Member of Gray Raven. Somewhat aloof in manner. Good at computers and machines, he is responsible for Gray Raven's hardware and technical issues.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has strong single attack ability.', 'Attack DMG boosting skill.']
DetailDes: The leader of Gray Raven. Brave and selfless, she is ever at the frontline of the war against the Corrupted.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has strong area attack ability.', 'Has ally healing skills.']
DetailDes: A member of Gray Raven. As one of the newest support Constructs, she's the anchor of the team.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has strong single attack ability.', 'Has shorter Cooldown of Signature Moves.']
DetailDes: Leader of the Purifying Force, elegant yet cold, always performing her orders to perfection.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Reduces damage taken.', 'Shields all damages within the range of Signature Moves.']
DetailDes: Fun-loving yet mysterious and elusive, her hobby is observing humans, with a practical joke or two mixed in.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Blocking skill.', 'Releases a shield to defend.']
DetailDes: Member of Strike Hawk, an outstanding solo operator. He is friendly and helpful, but his carelessness always gets him into trouble.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.', 'Signature Move can switch attacking forms.']
DetailDes: Trained at the Cosmos Technicians Union, a member of the Engineering Force, Karenina has a fiery personality and solves problems by blowing them up, something that the Purifying Force always finds useful.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has strong single attack ability.', 'Attacks at the back deal Extra Damage.']
DetailDes: Leader of the Forsaken, who chose to leave Babylonia to protect Oasis with his comrades who have been forgotten by the world.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has strong single attack ability.', 'Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.']
DetailDes: Lucia's signature frame. As graceful as it is powerful, its mere appearance on the battlefield inspires its allies, earning it the "Dawn" sobriquet.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has ally healing skills.', 'Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.']
DetailDes: Liv has cut her hair as a statement of her strong will to return to the battlefield.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.', 'Signature Move can switch attacking forms.']
DetailDes: The result of Kamui's control over the Tenebrion that he was imbued with. This frame is able to switch freely between the two battle forms.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has ally healing skills.', 'Signature Move can reduce the damage taken by allies.']
DetailDes: Behind the strength of Liv's heart is a simple dream, and such purity is why this frame is so powerful.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Easy to deal high combo damage.', 'Skill combinations are powerful.']
DetailDes: The limits have been broken. Past and present intertwine. Lee dominates the battlefield with superior computing power.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has strong area attack ability.', 'Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.']
DetailDes: Taking off her jacket and releasing the weapon restriction, Karenina is able to unleash the full force of her flaming wrath to burn away everything in her way.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.', 'Able to reduce Elemental Resistance of enemies.']
DetailDes: Nanami's enhanced model, equipped with IR-005 propulsion wheels, allowing her to speed across the battlefield at ease. "Hehe, you can only see Nanami's afterimages now."

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has strong single attack ability.', 'Skills can switch attacking modes.']
DetailDes: A mysterious enemy encountered by Gray Raven in City 015. Powerful yet mercurial.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to transport across space instantly.', 'Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.']
DetailDes: A frame specially designed to control spacecraft. It was used by Watanabe when he served in the Task Force.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ["Able to draw enemies' aggression.", 'Releases a shield to defend.']
DetailDes: An Archaeology Team member from the World Government Association of Art in Babylonia. The "new blood" of Babylonia. Loves art with a passion.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals great area damage.', 'Able to deal Physical and Elemental DMG.']
DetailDes: An illegally modified frame born during the time when the Construct tech was not mature. It can cause charge separation to produce lightning as a means of attack. Specializes in long-distance sniping.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to pull enemies in an area together.', 'Has ally healing skills.']
DetailDes: External support for Gray Raven, Sophia also functions as an envoy for the Akdilek Commercial Alliance. Born an orphan on the Eternal Engine, now the sharpest blade of its leader Jamilah.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Signature Move can switch attacking forms.', 'Releases a shield to defend.']
DetailDes: The leader of the Strike Hawk. Capable of relaying important intel through a secure and stable channel. He values the flawless completion of missions, and also the safety of all his teammates.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has sustained damage output.', 'Skills can switch attacking modes.']
DetailDes: Babylonia developed this latest frame specifically for Lucia based on Gray Raven's experience and the data collected from Alpha.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has shorter Cooldown of Signature Moves.', 'Has ally healing skills.']
DetailDes: Leader of Cerberus, and the backbone of Babylonia's long-range connection field test team. Vera's extreme methods and belligerent, elusive demeanor have put her at the center of many a controversy.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Signature Move can switch attacking forms.', 'Switch forms for high burst.']
DetailDes: A Transcendant that was once a repressed alter-ego in Kamui's M.I.N.D., Camu has been given his own unit by Babylonia, and now specializes in operations in and around heavily-Corrupted Dead Zones.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce Physical Defense of enemies.', 'Energy spheres provide great burst potential.']
DetailDes: Leader of the original Forest Guard, Rosetta has been taken in by Babylonia, designated as a special unit, and redeployed onto the battlefield in a more humanoid form.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals Extra DMG when Core Passive is activated.', 'Summons a Pet to attack when using a Signature Move.']
DetailDes: A Transcendant and the last head of Kowloong. After the Battle of Kowloong, she has gone into hiding and continued with her ambition to achieve the Tabula Akasha.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Uses follow-up skills to deal DMG and accumulate Energy', 'Deals continuous DMG after performing a Signature Move.']
DetailDes: Born in Kowloong and a former member of the theater. He has become a bodyguard on Asslam after many twists and turns.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Use 3-Ping to trigger 3-Ping and amass energy.', 'Her core form grants high burst and gains energy.']
DetailDes: As an Agent of the Ascension-Network, this is her complete combat form, in which she can manipulate the Heteromer energy of the Punishing Virus and Constructs to deliver attacks with a power that transcends all Ascendants.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Core state deals continuous high frequency damage.', 'Able to quickly recover energy for A2, 9S and itself.']
DetailDes: 2B is an all-purpose battle android from the automated YoRHa infantry. She is equipped with a multitude of blades for close-quarters combat and can attack from range using the POD support system.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to heal allies.', 'Able to hack enemies, dealing massive DMG.']
DetailDes: This unit's official title is Model S, Number 9. While this YoRHa member possesses offensive capabilities, he specializes in survey missions—and is particularly skilled at information gathering and hacking.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce enemy Defense.', 'Able to enhance herself, granting 2B and 9S increased DMG.']
DetailDes: A YoRHa prototype that specializes in close-quarter combat. Though not presently in use, it was originally created to speed along the implementation of other official models such as 2B and 9S.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to heal friendly force.', 'Able to precisely snipe the enemy after dodge']
DetailDes: As a Strike Hawk member, Wanshi always has a sleepy look. But once you get to know him better, you will realize he can be very trustworthy when things have gone bad.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to affect the game through different orb ping.', 'Able to switch to Signature Move status in a quick manner']
DetailDes: Formerly a member of the Archaeological Team, Selena used to have a great singing voice. She was also known for her talent in art and her gentle yet resilient nature. After being rescued by an Ascendant following the space station and Red Tide incidents, she is now a Transcendant.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to switch to a burst form and launch powerful attacks.', 'Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.']
DetailDes: The second specialized frame of Babylonia's mid-term military Construct development plan. It has been adjusted and optimized based on Chrome's request.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['A signature move that can deal massive DMG.', 'Can remove abnormal status effects when in Haywire status.']
DetailDes: Originally a subject of a Daedalus corporation experiment, she was retrieved during a mission conducted by Kurono. Later, she was transferred to Babylonia's Task Force with Vera. She is gloomy and seemingly expressionless in appearance. However, she becomes exceptionally vicious and dangerous under extreme circumstances.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.']
DetailDes: A frame Vera used in the past. Designed as an advanced, decisive countermeasure against hostile Constructs, it was finally introduced as an official unit not long ago. Its weapon is a specially forged banner spear.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Can deal various combos.', 'Signature Move can switch attacking forms.']
DetailDes: A former performer in the Golden Age who is sarcastic on the outside yet serious on the inside. Participated in a lot of actions as an Ascendant. Reformed into the current frame by an agent due to huge damage done to the old frame after a few number of setbacks.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Enhances teammates.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: A brand new specialized frame developed by the Science Council that is capable of "purifying" the Punishing Virus. To protect everything she loves, Liv has made her own choice.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Enhances teammates.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: Selena's backup frame. Made with the support of an artist from WGAA, it is free-spirited and lively like its namesake, but the sentiments it embodies are earnest and solemn.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Uses her Signature Move to summon her weapon.', 'Deals massive DMG with Core Passive Follow-Up']
DetailDes: The frame of Pulao, one of the Dragon Children, is not made from conventional components but has been carefully adapted to fit her M.I.N.D., allowing her to make the most of her unusually strong powers.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Signature Move can switch attacking forms.', 'Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.']
DetailDes: A frame Nanami made for herself. It is extremely lightweight, but both the technology inside it and its strength have reached a level that is far beyond the level of the human technology nowadays.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Freezes enemies to restrain their actions.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: A mechanoid from the Church of Machina that roams Earth in search of the Sagemachina. Compared with other mechanoids, she seems to have other reasons for pursuing this "Sage".

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.']
DetailDes: A frame Karenina developed for the low-gravity environment on the Moon. The core power system is equipped with a cutting-edge miniaturized gravitation device, allowing for short-term air mobility.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Activates Core Passive repeatedly to deal massive DMG.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: The frame "he" created in order to save Noan. It weighed only 41.3 kg at first. A lot of deteriorated parts were used to restrict the movement of the user. Babylonia remodeled it to ensure everything could run smoothly.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to switch to a burst form and launch powerful attacks.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: A new specialized frame devised by Kurono based on thorough research into the tissue of the Hetero-Hive Mother. It is equipped with the Phantom Tracer, which can decipher certain information left by the Punishing Virus.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG by activating Core Passive repeatedly.', 'Signature Move can deal massive DMG.']
DetailDes: A frame that has undergone a series of optimizations and modifications based on the Construct Kurono created during the early years. She has become an important member of the Egret squad since she started serving with the Task Force.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Casts the 3-Ping Skill at high frequency to deal massive damage.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: A new specialized frame created using the information from the Heteromer Shard and the research materials of the Inver-Device. This creation boasts a certain level of expertise in deciphering the Punishing Language.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Enhances teammates.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: A new frame developed by Ayla as a chief developer. With state-of-the-art technical support from the WGAA, it maintains Ayla's signature style while ensuring its battle performance does not pale even beside combat-specialized frames.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Skills can switch attacking modes.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: Having experienced Ascension-Network's fluctuations, she walks the earth in a new form. Her changes are unknown, but her enhanced power is undeniable.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Has ally healing skills.', 'Able to enhance herself and grant Pulao and Qu extra buffs.']
DetailDes: A mechanoid from Kowloong now waking up from her long sleep in the Church of Machina. Perfectly showcasing the fruit of Kowloong's machine technology through her appearance that extremely resembles a human being, she is still moving around as a mechanoid.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Enhances teammates.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: A new frame designed by Kurono with supervision from the Science Council. Customized to stabilize No. 21's M.I.N.D., it grants a massive increase in battle power while providing M.I.N.D. stability.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG by activating Core Passive repeatedly.', 'Signature Moves can deal massive DMG.']
DetailDes: One of the Cerberus members. He was forced to leave the Purifying Force due to a mysterious conspiracy, but has now become a sharp fang of the three-headed hound.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Enhances teammates.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: Possesses a special Aurora Squadron-made biological weapon armor "sister" capable of M.I.N.D. connection. Now, Echo is traveling on the boundless ground in the pursuit of true justice.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'Can switch Attack Modes for Signature Move.']
DetailDes: Lamia's new frame designed by Luna with the Ascendant abilities. Enhanced based on Lamia's old frame, it is capable of switching freely between the human form and the mermaid form. Although Lamia whispered that she wanted a 170cm height, her human form height was only designed to be 169cm.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'Has a certain level of endurance.']
DetailDes: A mysterious girl with a blue flame in her left eye and a giant cannon, who has traveled countless worlds.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.', 'Deals massive DMG in a short time.']
DetailDes: A frame independently developed by the Forsaken for tough battles with a brand-new design of the M.I.N.D. carrier module.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'Has a certain level of endurance.']
DetailDes: A frame reforged by Tabula Akasha through life and death even with the Transcendant's Punishing Virus removed. Its principle and structure remain unknown.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ["Able to heal and boost allies' Dark DMG.", "Able to rapidly break the enemy's Equilibrium Field."]
DetailDes: Vice-captain of the Engineering Force. Since she is a programming expert, the core configurations of her frame are geared more toward a technician. However, this doesn't mean that she's not capable of combat—her stage is far beyond the battlefield in the physical world.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Skills can switch attacking modes.', "Able to rapidly break the enemy's Equilibrium Field."]
DetailDes: Once an agent of the Ascension-Network, she now seeks to resist, guide, and control the entire Ascension-Network to create an ideal paradise after the Agent Zero incident.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.', 'Launches the enemy into the Combustible status and Ignites them.']
DetailDes: A balanced duel-purpose frame capable of both attack and defense that the Science Council specially designed for the Support Force. It carries many special parts with part of its features adjusted accordingly.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce Physical Defense of enemies.', 'This skill can unleash the Ultima Slash.']
DetailDes: This frame, forged by the Church of Machina, is equipped with new hardware while preserving the superior instruction set architecture of Kowloong from the Golden Age. Though fierce in battle, the core of Hanying remains gentle and kind, providing her with the strength to stand firm.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce the Ice Resistance of enemies.', 'This skill can trigger the Glaciation effect.']
DetailDes: This Tank frame is equipped with an advanced auto-aiming system while retaining some medical devices that are usually exclusive to Support frames. After retrieving all of his memory data, Wanshi has grown into a more complete version of himself. Though the long dream has yet to end, his path forward has already become clear.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time', 'Skills can trigger the Plasma Beam Effect.']
DetailDes: Developed based on years of research of the Science Council, Pyroath is a new specialized frame carrying the Omega Core with efficient air combat capability. Through countless moments with Gray Raven, Lucia has found her purpose. Now, she's determined and calm just like the fire that forever burns on the frame.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time', 'Skills can trigger the Glaciation Effect.']
DetailDes: Following the style of the Yata human era, this unit is specifically designed for extended combat operations. Equipped with high-performance plasma armatures in its arm structure and rear-mounted mechanical arms, it can unleash devastating kinetic energy in an instant.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce the Lightning and Fire Resistance of enemies.', 'Launches the enemy into the Combustible status and Ignites them.']
DetailDes: Designed by Nanami herself, this frame features a deep-space specialized protective coating, allowing her to barely withstand the corrosive surface environment of the Red Tide while also possessing exceptional interstellar navigation capabilities.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Character ability changes based on the team formation.', "Able to rapidly break the enemy's Equilibrium Field."]
DetailDes: Along with the rise and fall of countless civilizations, this is where Ishmael's choices intersect. This frame was born from a cosmos beyond time with materials beyond human comprehension, as enigmatic as the will of the Observer that operates within.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Grants the power of healing and making allies deal more damage.', 'Skills can trigger the Plasma Beam Effect.']
DetailDes: The convergence of Las Prados's wealth and Project Winter's technologies coalesced into this frame. Its eerie quality emanates not merely from the Ascension-Network's favor but more profoundly from the ambitions and desires deep inside her M.I.N.D., along with secrets buried in history's obscured chapters.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'Skills can trigger the Glaciation Effect.']
DetailDes: A specialized frame co-developed by the Science Council and the World Government Association of Art with improved stability of M.I.N.D. to deal with Transcendants. The adaptee can use it with a suppression device to perform combat skills of multiple parts playing simultaneously.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'Launches the enemy into the Combustible status and Ignites them.']
DetailDes: Say goodbye to the warm cradle and confront the painful awakening—she has traversed infinite loops to enter the real world with the full might of the matrix.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Grants the power of healing and making allies deal more damage.', 'Skills can trigger the Darkflow Effect.']
DetailDes: A test frame developed by Kurono. It failed the berserk test after activation and was abandoned during a mission. Years later, Vera reactivated the frame, seized its control after fierce combats and chaos, and named it "Geiravor".

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'This skill can unleash the Ultima Slash.']
DetailDes: A legendary devil swordsman who masters lightning-fast quick-draw techniques. The elder twin of Dante.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Deals massive DMG in a short time.', 'Launches the enemy into the Combustible status and Ignites them.']
DetailDes: The boss of Devil May Cry, and the most powerful devil hunter alive. Revered for his legendary strength.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.', 'Skills can trigger the Raydiance Effect.']
DetailDes: This is a new specialized frame developed by the Science Council, based on further validation of the Phantom Tracer. It can disrupt Punishing information to some extent, effectively weakening its influence.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.', 'This skill can unleash the Ultima Slash.']
DetailDes: A new frame designed by Babylonia. Compared to Kurono's older model, its M.I.N.D. is less stable, with output levels prone to wide fluctuations.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Grants the power of healing and making allies deal more damage', 'Skills can trigger the Ignition Effect.']
DetailDes: A former member of the Church of Machina, who left the organization for various reasons and now operates independently. Prefers expressing herself through force rather than words.

ObtainSpeicalDes: ['Able to reduce the Resistance of enemies.', 'Skills can trigger the Darkflow Effect.']
DetailDes: Developed by the Science Council, this new frame integrates data from the Golden Age's Phylotree of Ousia project into the M.I.N.D. Its success marks the dawn of a new era.
